management\" style=\"color:#CC1B2A;text-decoration:underline;\">\u2696\ufe0f Weight Management</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;padding-bottom:0;\"><a href=\"https://www.bargainchemist.co.nz/collections/baby\" style=\"color:#CC1B2A;text-decoration:underline;\">\ud83d\udc76 Baby</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;padding-bottom:0;\"><a href=\"https://www.bargainchemist.co.nz/collections/personal-care\" style=\"color:#CC1B2A;text-decoration:underline;\">\ud83d\udec1 Personal Care</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;padding-bottom:0;\"><a href=\"https://www.bargainchemist.co.nz/collections/cold-flu\" style=\"color:#CC1B2A;text-decoration:underline;\">\ud83e\udd27 Cold &amp; Flu</a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n<!-- PRICE BEAT -->\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#fff5f5;padding:20px 30px;\">\n<p style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#FF0031;text-align:center;margin:0 0 6px 0;padding-bottom:0;\">\ud83c\udfc6 Price Beat Guarantee</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555555;line-height:1.6;text-align:center;margin:0;padding-bottom:0;\">Find it cheaper at another NZ pharmacy? We'll beat the price by 10% \u2014 guaranteed.</p>\n</td></tr>\n<!-- DIVIDER -->\n<tr><td style=\"background-color:#ffffff;padding:0 30px;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td style=\"border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;font-size:0;height:1px;\"> </td></tr></table></td></tr>\n<!-- SOCIAL -->\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;padding:24px 30px 28px 30px;\">\n<p style=\"font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;color:#222222;text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px 0;padding-bottom:0;\">Get social with us!</p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n<td style=\"padding:0 8px;\"><a href=\"https://tiktok.com/@bargainchemistnz\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img alt=\